===================================================================
 God Module combine elements of EBM, Techno, Darkwave and Synth    
 Pop to create a style of music that is as powerful as it is       
 melodic. Pounding beats mix with unforgettable synth hooks and    
 creatively effected vocals to make up the sound that has taken    
 the underground electronic music scene by storm.                  
                                                                   
 God Module brings a small but impressive discography with them to 
 Sector 9 Studios. Their debut CD Artificial was deemed as one of  
 the most impressive debuts in the electro world in years.
